Package de.hsrt.holbox.Economics

Class MatrixElement

java.lang.Object
de.hsrt.holbox.Economics.MatrixElement
public class MatrixElement extends Object
Author:
benelhen This class defines a matrix with elements that contains :1. Nr. PV, 2. Nr. Bat, 3. Nr DG, 4. Nr.WT, 4. concemption DG 5. powerflow (Boolean) powerflow a boolean to check the feasability of the combination of PV, DG, WT and Batteries 6. LCOE is the calculated LCOE for this combination
